org.apache.flink.mesos.runtime.clusterframework

类 MesosTaskManagerParameters

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.apache.flink.mesos.runtime.clusterframework.MesosTaskManagerParameters

  • public class MesosTaskManagerParameters
extends java.lang.Object
    This class describes the Mesos-specific parameters for launching a TaskManager process.

    These parameters are in addition to the common parameters provided by ContaineredTaskManagerParameters.
